                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> d<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>ae</abbr></expan> Lun<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="2"/>Marcellinius <lb n="3"/>Placidinus <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ivium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>R</abbr><ex>omanorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Mog</abbr><ex>ontiaci</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>et Mar<supplied reason="lost">ti</supplied>nia <lb n="6"/>Martina <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>ater</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>ex voto <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuerunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aeti</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>Tacito et Aemi<lb break="no" n="9"/>liano co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">K</supplied>al</abbr><ex>endis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iun</abbr><ex>iis</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fundjahr: 1808 oder 1809. In zwei Teile gebrochen. Auf der linken Nebenseite ein Blitzbündel, auf der rechten urceus und patera. Z. 1 befindet sich auf der corona. (B): CIL 13, 06733; ILS 7079; Selzer; Frenz: kleinere Leseabweichungen.</p>
            </div>
